Details:
Welcome to St. Catherine Institute of Management & Technology, New Delhi. SCIMT has been established in the hustling, busting Capital City. This Institution is the dream projects of its Founder Chairperson Mrs. Catherine Ince, a visionary, an acknowledged educationist and a staunchly dedicated social worker.
St. Catherine Institute of Management & Technology is an institution dedicated to creating industry-ready managerial talent. SCIMT offers training in Indias exponentially growing verticals - Marketing, Information Technology, Retail, Finance and Financial Services and International Management as well as a host of other new emerging fields.
The Institute is run on principles of efficiency, dedication, integrity and effectiveness. The core team, drawn from across diverse disciplines of Academics has proven track records of success in their chosen area of specialization.
St. Catherine Institute of Management & Technology aims to prepare the students to be successful in the changing workplace, to equip them with technical knowledge and capabilities, flexibility, and an understanding of the societal context of the corporate world. We give the students, support and encouragement which they need to reach their full potential.
